This product implements the following W3C and IETF specifications:

    Verifiable Credentials Data Model (VCDM) 2.0    https://www.w3.org/TR/vc-data-model-2.0/
    Verifiable Credential Data Integrity 1.0        https://www.w3.org/TR/vc-data-integrity/
    Securing VCs using JOSE and COSE 1.0            https://www.w3.org/TR/vc-jose-cose/
    Bitstring Status List 1.0                       https://www.w3.org/TR/vc-bitstring-status-list/
    DI BBS Cryptosuites (bbs-2023)                  https://www.w3.org/TR/vc-di-bbs/
    SD-JWT (RFC 9901) and SD-JWT VC (draft-ietf-oauth-sd-jwt-vc-16)
    JSON Schema 2020-12

Conformance is measured against the W3C VCDM 2.0 test suite
(https://github.com/w3c/vc-data-model-2.0-test-suite); the honest pass status
and known limitations are documented in docs/conformance.md.
